name: Didi Pache
description: I became licensed in 2010 after an extensive history inluxury sales & executive management. Born in the Los Angeles area, I have acquired, sold, built, remodeled & leased homes in Los Angeles and San Francisco Bay Area, Dallas, Boston and Omaha (where I have lived since 1996).Known for an exuberant personality and passion for Omaha, I am easy to work with, always willing to take the time to discuss my clients concerns, and have first-hand experience in the relocation process. I maintain a strong educational foundation having earned The Graduate, REALTOR(r) Institute Designation (GRI), providing a more in-depth training in legal/regulatory issues, technology, professional standards, and the sales process. I am military friendly and hold the MRP certificate as well. Married for 30+ years with two sons; one is a Marine Veteran the other is currently serving in theNavy. In my spare time, I enjoy my 3 grandsons, travelling, photography,cooking and reading.time. REALTOR, GRI, MRP, VALC, SFR, E-Certified, Notary
